# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore build artifacts and unnecessary files
bin/
dist/
.git/
.github/
docs/
examples/
hack/
test/
*.md
*.tape
*.gif
*.mp4
*.svg
*.png

# Keep test files out of the image
**/*_test.go

# Keep Go module cache out
.cache/
